Get Rosters

Source: R/3_rosters.R
ffs_rosters.Rd

This function lightly wraps ffscrapr::ff_rosters() and adds fantasypros_id, which is a required column for ffsimulator.

a dataframe of rosters that includes a fantasypros_id column
